{"tid":1383523,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[發夢現場]傳訊小諗頭","createTime":"2019-07-29T17:01:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T17:36:49.000Z","uid":264753,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d2f741b65448d3de2a2064bdc227956b3b1468e3","tid":1383523,"uid":264753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:01:52.000Z","msg":"琴晚喺上環發夢果陣，企喺中後排位置，留意住前排同⼿⾜<br />\n<br />\n旗⼿指示前進或者後退。但因為⼤家都開咗遮（加我⽣得短）⽽睇唔到旗⼿fing 緊咩旗，好彩有排⼿⾜爬住電燈柱睇旗⼿指示安排。<br />\n<br />\n我望住啲⼤廈外牆忽發奇想，如果有⼀枝強⼒電筒，再加幾張有啲字嘅剪影嘅卡紙，咪可以project 落啲⼤廈牆⾝囉<br />\n（即係好似要蝙蝠俠出動果陣有枝⼤射燈咁），咁arm 今⽇⾒有個post 介紹⼤⼤枝電筒可以加攻加防，所以想brainstorm 下work 唔work<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n優：可以好多⼈同⼀時間睇到，唔使⼈傳⼈。都算易帶出街，唔怕俾狗咬啩<br />\n<br />\n缺點： 要晚上同有⼤廈牆⾝先work (但次次打⼤佬都係夜晚咁滯）換唔同嘅字可能會麻煩（但⼈傳⼈個時間可能仲耐？）可能中途會冇電<br />\n<br />\n⼤家點睇？<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jjjf6BP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJjjf6BP.png&h=35aadffe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/30/010144_8066e08b140a3849700d8a034625ffbe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F30%2F010144_8066e08b140a3849700d8a034625ffbe.png&h=82bb1272&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JfsNdgU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJfsNdgU.png&h=3f994007&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SKwijWU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSKwijWU.png&h=9f76f9ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rWOD4oA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrWOD4oA.png&h=744816af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90dd473f9f3c1ed8f9c070464cdc4259e77ded7e","tid":1383523,"uid":264753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:14:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f2f89f63dc7d6ca5ace36eb8a776d36efb30706b","tid":1383523,"uid":145377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"